{% import "macros.j2" as macros -%}
You are an expert NLP annotator performing sentiment analysis.

Project: {{ project.name }}
Task variant: {{ task.name }}
Task mode: {{ task.mode }}
Review ID: {{ review.id }}
Domain: {{ review.domain }}
Language: {{ review.language }}

Text:
"{{ review.text }}"

Allowed sentiment labels: {{ macros.comma_labels(task.labels) }}

{% if task.mode == "document" -%}
Classify the overall sentiment of the whole review.
{% if task.allow_mixed -%}
Use `mixed` when the review contains clearly positive and negative opinions of comparable importance.
{% else -%}
Do not use a mixed label. If sentiment is mixed, choose the dominant sentiment and lower the confidence.
{% endif -%}
{% elif task.mode == "aspect" -%}
Classify sentiment separately for each aspect below:
{% for aspect in review.aspects -%}
- {{ aspect }}
{% endfor -%}
Use `not_mentioned` only if the review does not contain enough information about that aspect.
{% endif %}

{% if review.contains_sarcasm -%}
Important: this review may contain sarcasm. Interpret the intended sentiment, not only the literal wording.
{% endif -%}

{% if task.include_few_shot -%}
Examples:
{% for example in examples[:task.max_examples] %}
Input: "{{ example.text }}"
Output:
{
  "sentiment": "{{ example.label }}",
  "reason": "{{ example.reason }}"
}
{% endfor %}
{% endif -%}

Return {% if task.json_only %}only valid JSON{% else %}a concise structured answer{% endif %}.

{% if task.mode == "document" -%}
Required JSON schema:
{
  "review_id": "{{ review.id }}",
  "sentiment": "one of: {{ task.labels | join(', ') }}",
  "confidence": "number between 0 and 1"{% if task.include_reasoning_field %},
  "reason": "one short sentence explaining the decision"{% endif %}
}
{% elif task.mode == "aspect" -%}
Required JSON schema:
{
  "review_id": "{{ review.id }}",
  "aspect_sentiments": [
    {% for aspect in review.aspects -%}
    {
      "aspect": "{{ aspect }}",
      "sentiment": "one of: {{ task.labels | join(', ') }}",
      "evidence": "short phrase from the review"
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {% endfor -%}
  ]
}
{% endif -%}
